methods.name: reStakeFromSnitch
methods.desc: Follow up operation called by the snitched App to perform restaking of the delegated Algo clawed back

args.name: snitchedApp
args.desc: The AppID of the validator to snitch

args.name: receiverApp
args.desc: The AppID of the receiver of the delegated Algo

args.name: restakeTxn
args.desc: The PayTxn following the snitch that sends the delegated Algo to be moved back and restaked
